parameters: Mage Relm: Please don't move around on your own!

Informant Leon: Take a look! It's not just a cave, it's
undoubtedly an ancient ruins!

Mage Relm: It seems to be certain. The patterns depicted are
related to the alchemical demon, Beton.

Mage Relm: What's the matter? Have you just noticed my
genius now?

Thief Nora: I can't quite put it into words, but I can sense
a [scent of death] coming from here...
Thief Nora: C-Can't we turn back?

Informant Leon: We can't just come all this way and turn
back!

Informant Leon: Now, let's proceed towards the deepest part
of the ruins!

Mage Relm: That's why, don't go off on your own! It defeats
the purpose of having guards, you know!?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
